!! Coffee Freshness Indicators

Configure when coffee is considered at peak freshness:

|!Setting |!Days After Roast |
|Peak Freshness Starts |<$edit-text tiddler="$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/peak-start" tag="input" default="7"/> days |
|Peak Freshness Ends |<$edit-text tiddler="$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/peak-end" tag="input" default="21"/> days |
|Still Good Until |<$edit-text tiddler="$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/optimal-end" tag="input" default="60"/> days |

''Guidelines:''

* ''Very Fresh'' (< <$text text={{{ [[$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/peak-start]get[text]] ~[[7]] }}}/> days): Coffee is still degassing
* ''Peak'' (<$text text={{{ [[$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/peak-start]get[text]] ~[[7]] }}}/>-<$text text={{{ [[$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/peak-end]get[text]] ~[[21]] }}}/> days): Optimal flavor development
* ''Good'' (<$text text={{{ [[$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/peak-end]get[text]] ~[[21]] }}}/>-<$text text={{{ [[$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/optimal-end]get[text]] ~[[60]] }}}/> days): Still enjoyable
* ''Aging'' (> <$text text={{{ [[$:/plugins/mblackman/coffee-tracker/config/freshness/optimal-end]get[text]] ~[[60]] }}}/> days): Flavor declining

